# Flexfoot - online shoes store (e-commerce website)

FlexFoot is an online shoe shopping website developed using **Odoo ERP**.  
This project demonstrates the working of an e-commerce platform including product display, cart system, and payment integration.

---

## ğŸ“Œ Project Objective
To design and develop an online shoe store where users can:
- Browse products
- View product details
- Add products to cart
- Place orders online
- Experience a simple and responsive UI

